# OIS API Intelligence Database
**Outside Inn Studios | E.I. Werner Brand**
*Living document — March 2026*

> **Purpose:** Primary and secondary source intelligence on every platform API relevant to OIS operations. One document per platform. Built for someone with Notion fluency and AI-assisted coding capability. Every integration decision traces back to a source in here.

> **Build Order (Bottom of Doc):** Start with Fourthwall → Discord webhook. Everything else follows.

> **Verification log:**
> - v1.0 — March 4, 2026: Initial build from official docs (8 platforms)
> - v1.1 — March 4, 2026: Enriched from verified external research. Added: Notion `Notion-Version: 2025-09-03` mandatory header; Notion Markdown API (official); Notion multi-source DB `data_source_id`; Notion file upload limits; YouTube `liveChatMessages.streamList` server-streaming method; Fourthwall Open API beta + Platform OAuth invite-only caveat + Merchant Center RSS feed; Discord Feb 23 2026 permission split breaking change; OBS v5 protocol break from v4; Streamlabs 60-min token expiry + v2 alerts endpoint.

